n house, Chika Evans, on Monday appeared in a Grade I Area Court, Karu, FCT, for alleged negligence. January 11, 2021 In "News" A 20-year-old security guard, Joseph Tioko, on Monday appeared in a Karu Grade I Area Court, Abuja,  for allegedly stealing a cow September 16, 2019 In "News" The police on Monday arraigned five accused persons in a Karu Grade 1 Area Court, Abuja for allegedly stealing their roommate’s cell phone worth N76,000. The defendants are standing trial on a two-count charge of joint acts and theft to which they denied committing the offence. The accused persons are:… December 21, 2020 In "News"